saxer-mail-extractor
====================

Description
-----------
saxer-mail-extractor is a set of scripts which extract mail-addresses
recursively from sources.  The main script is written in Perl and
extracts addresses from either plain, JSON or PDF source files.
It supports two modes of operation currently: basic and incremental.

Requirements
------------
perl
CAM::PDF
Email::Address
Email::Valid
File::Type
JSON
Net::IDN::Encode
Time::Local

Documentation
-------------
See POD (Plain Old Documentation) file: docs/mail_extractor.pod.

Usage example
-------------
$ ./app/mail_extractor.pl -c ./config/mail_extractor.cfg --parse-pdf

